	* All GNUmakefiles: added GNUSTEP_CORE_SOFTWARE=YES at the
	beginning.
	* GNUmakefile: Export GNUSTEP_CORE_SOFTWARE to reduce chances of a
	problem if a GNUmakefile in a subdirectory is missing it.
	
